cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Network Latency and L2 Forwarding Performance Tests with Variable Packet Rates
  and Sizes on nida and cesis Nodes
abstract: This dataset captures Layer 2 network latency and forwarding performance
  measurements under varying packet rates and sizes, using Moongen-based load generation
  and Lua-driven workload execution. The experiment evaluates hardware response times,
  energy consumption, and synchronization accuracy across six runs per configuration.
  Setup scripts ensure consistent environments for testing, while looped commands
  generate traffic, capture latency histograms, and produce synchronized timing logs.
  Results include CSV and PNG files for analyzing throughput, latency distributions,
  and power metrics under different workload conditions.
